{{flavour|This scroll places a curse on a worn piece of armour.}}

Reading a '''scroll of curse armour''' will [[curse]] a worn piece of [[armour]] of your choosing, allowing you to receive [[Ashenzari]]'s defensive skill boosts and improving the rate at which you gain piety from him. They do not generate naturally, but Ashenzari-worshipers can produce them by praying over a [[scroll of remove curse]].

==History==
*In [[0.18]], Ashenzari's ability to create these scrolls was removed in favor of the more straightforward "curse item" ability.
*Prior to [[0.14]], scrolls of curse armour would be naturally generated as loot, just like any other [[scroll]].
